{"tid":123772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李偲嫣持「驚人錄音」追薪","createTime":"2017-02-17T05:23:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T08:29:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0a9580e06af3342f1675c9beb1119c047b2a769f","tid":123772,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T05:23:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170217/19930974\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170217%2F19930974&d=bJSHN4a6RFajNgW6euKvYU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=8940418e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170217%2F19930974&h=ea688c4a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170217/19930974</a><br />\n<br />\n李偲嫣持「驚人錄音」追薪<br />\n<br />\n8,541<br />\n ■李偲嫣昨戴鴨嘴帽低調到庭。<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n■李偲嫣昨戴鴨嘴帽低調到庭。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】撐警大聯盟召集人、正義聯盟創黨主席李偲嫣，稱遭兩間網媒公司拖欠前年12月的半個月薪金，昨變身苦主入稟勞資審裁處，追討欠薪、代通知金及有薪年假等共約15.8萬元。公司否認雙方有僱傭關係，稱只屬合作夥伴，一早協定只出佣金而無月薪，批評李偲嫣行事出爾反爾。李聲言手持一段「驚人錄音」能證明雙方主僕關係。<br />\n<br />\n自稱月薪5.7萬<br />\n申索人李偲嫣昨戴鴨嘴帽隻身低調到庭，聆訊全程無脫下帽子。兩被告公司「網購無限」（前稱匯傳媒）及「媒體無限」由同一名董事、中華總商會會董張俊勇代表，張俊勇在庭上表明無意和解。自稱月薪5.7萬元的李偲嫣沒披露「驚人錄音」內容，但在庭外補充指為被告公司分別擔任行政總裁及總監。<br />\n但據了解，公司一方稱沒與李訂定任何月薪出糧協議，所謂5.7萬元月薪只是以往預先發放佣金的平均約數。案件4月再訊。<br />\n案件編號：LBTC297/17<br />\n■記者伍嘉豪  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n輔警涉勒索女友　辯稱做場戲"},{"pid":"aba9fb2a8738b6892064ab80c757ad5e3d0b32af","tid":123772,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T05:24:29.000Z","msg":"■李偲嫣昨戴鴨嘴帽低調到庭<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170217/large/17ls3p4a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170217%2Flarge%2F17ls3p4a.jpg&h=ee866435&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6e768db727bd992830614e7458a8524311fc9cd","tid":123772,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T05:26:26.000Z","msg":"呢隻臭老雞真係成日搏出位"},{"pid":"20d271216e0e71fa41ba4bc22b2592fc5210a2b8","tid":123772,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T05:30:35.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇簽contract應該冇得追<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  即管放多d料出黎娛樂下大家lo"},{"pid":"6f8b19059b22778560b84ea72845eaf6f45bfc56","tid":123772,"uid":61533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T05:38:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b995aaec4d673ccef6301626313b9f144aec4675","tid":123772,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T06:05:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d2132f0f0d45dff6159680fa666754e4f3bb8c1","tid":123772,"uid":67657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T06:40:52.000Z","msg":"正宗肥西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e594bec9bec0331e7d2cd30f6ce8ce2a13a82594","tid":123772,"uid":29273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T06:47:04.000Z","msg":"佢自己咪又係做雞"},{"pid":"c64f4e0682eeefdc5edf445e8e317a584d49ce93","tid":123772,"uid":77416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T06:48:52.000Z","msg":"唔夠維穩費? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c42e8ee7c3b6a995e4cecd69fec2a772c763e6c","tid":123772,"uid":22737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T06:49:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c765649f03199ec008523f6f6c5c29f42ea773b2","tid":123772,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T06:57:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.makeagif.com/media/1-29-2017/z3bHa3.gif\" data-th